title: DOWNLOAD: 2015 mid-year review and supplementary budget
text:
21 July 2015 20:01 CET DOWNLOAD: 2015 mid-year review and supplementary budget By Daily Guide 
Ghana's finance minister Seth Terkper has presented a mid-year review of the Budget and Supplementary Estimates for 2015. 
He also outlined a supplementary budget to the Lawmaking Chamber as well as measures being implemented to keep the economy healthy.
